{"title":"Stephen D&#8217;Onofrio&#8217;s Fruit Art","link":"https://kottke.org/24/03/stephen-donofrios-fruit-paintings","date":1710349776000,"content":"\n        <p><img src=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/donofriopileoffruitcopy.jpg\" srcset=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=500,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/donofriopileoffruitcopy.jpg 500w, /cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/donofriopileoffruitcopy.jpg 1200w\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"989\" height=\"514\" alt=\"donofriopileoffruitcopy.jpg\" /></p>\n\n<p>I recently discovered the “pile of fruit”-themed art of <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/stephenadonofrio/\">Stephen D’Onofrio</a>. The strawberries are a preliminary <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/C35HwSvrUro/\">sketch</a>, but they’re what drew me in, and the rest are paintings. He’s represented by Dallas’s <a href=\"https://www.galleriurbane.com/stephen-donofrio\">Galleri Urbane</a>. I also like his “<a href=\"https://www.galleriurbane.com/stephen-donofrio\">trees fitting exactly in the canvas</a>” paintings.</p>\n\n<p><img src=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/donofriofruitmorecopy.jpg\" srcset=\"/cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=500,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/donofriofruitmorecopy.jpg 500w, /cdn-cgi/image/format=auto,fit=scale-down,width=1200,metadata=none/plus/misc/images/donofriofruitmorecopy.jpg 1200w\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1000\" height=\"574\" alt=\"donofriofruitmorecopy.jpg\" /></p>\n\n <p><strong>Tags:</strong> <a href=\"https://kottke.org/tag/art\">art</a> · <a href=\"https://kottke.org/tag/fruit\">fruit</a> · <a href=\"https://kottke.org/tag/Stephen%20D%27Onofrio\">Stephen D’Onofrio</a></p>\n\n <p>💬 <a href=\"https://kottke.org/24/03/stephen-donofrios-fruit-paintings\">Join the discussion on kottke.org</a> →</p>\n\n    ","author":"Edith Zimmerman","siteTitle":"Kottke","siteHash":"89a883271b4598f9b33ebe87be70d38557bcd266e68aee521a8f93622e0ab723","entryHash":"4db91b91308a74a7232a95b66622344fc2c4dc3f23ffd0428b05bbcc72b5e644","category":"default"}